des:
I want to train at home, but I am not motivated. .
At such time, please use the skill saying "Alexa, open muscle exercises ".

People who are usually training, and those who are not
If you do muscle training along with this skill, you can drive the muscle to the limit in a short time.
Ask Alexa to cheer and instruct you not to give up on the way.

The current muscle training menu can be selected from "push-ups, abs and squats".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
